SubjectRemission Order in Respect of Non-residential Leases and Licences of Occupation Under the Administration of the Parks Canada Agency
PrecisREMISSION ORDER IN RESPECT OF NON-RESIDENTIAL AND LICENCES OF OCCUPATION UNDER THE ADMINISTRATION OF THE PARKS CANADA AGENCY in order to provide all Parks Canada Agency's commercial tenants the opportunity to apply for financial relief, on a portion of the annual rent, fees and interest during the COVID-19 outbreak period..
